{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/Datebase/queryset","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"44e1e0d4-008f-5fba-958d-858e08dac424","html":"<p>QuerySet은 장고에서 데이터베이스를 쉽게 다루기 위해서 사용하는 ORM 기능이다. <br>\n원하는 객체를 불러오거나 검색할 수 있다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"전체-객체-불러오기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%84%EC%B2%B4-%EA%B0%9D%EC%B2%B4-%EB%B6%88%EB%9F%AC%EC%98%A4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"전체 객체 불러오기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>전체 객체 불러오기</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">Model<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>objects<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">all</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"특정-객체-불러오기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B9%EC%A0%95-%EA%B0%9D%EC%B2%B4-%EB%B6%88%EB%9F%AC%EC%98%A4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"특정 객체 불러오기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>특정 객체 불러오기</h3>\n<p>get은 불러오려는 객체가 없으면 오류를 발생시키기 때문에 None 처리를 해줘야 한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">Model<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>objects<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>get<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token builtin\">id</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">None</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"객체가-존재하는지-확인truefalse\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9D%EC%B2%B4%EA%B0%80-%EC%A1%B4%EC%9E%AC%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%EC%A7%80-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8truefalse\" aria-label=\"객체가 존재하는지 확인truefalse permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>객체가 존재하는지 확인(True/False)</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">Model<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>objects<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token builtin\">id</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exists<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"조건을-걸어서-여러개의-객체-불러오기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4%EC%9D%84-%EA%B1%B8%EC%96%B4%EC%84%9C-%EC%97%AC%EB%9F%AC%EA%B0%9C%EC%9D%98-%EA%B0%9D%EC%B2%B4-%EB%B6%88%EB%9F%AC%EC%98%A4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"조건을 걸어서 여러개의 객체 불러오기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>조건을 걸어서 여러개의 객체 불러오기</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token comment\"># id가 2인 객체를 전부 불러오기</span>\nModel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>objects<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token builtin\">id</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># id가 2이고, title이 'hi'인 객체를 전부 불러오기</span>\nModel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>objects<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token builtin\">id</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> title<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'hi'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"filter에-옵션-주기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#filter%EC%97%90-%EC%98%B5%EC%85%98-%EC%A3%BC%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"filter에 옵션 주기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>filter에 옵션 주기</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>exact : 값 매칭</li>\n<li>iexact : 대소문자 구분없이 값 매칭</li>\n<li>startswith, istartswith : 해당 값으로 시작하는 결과 찾기</li>\n<li>endswith, iendswith(대소문자를 구분하지 않음) : 해당 값으로 끝나는 결과 찾기</li>\n<li>contains, icontains(대소문자를 구분하지 않음) : 값을 포함하는 결과 찾기</li>\n<li>gt : 컬럼 > 조건, 값보다 큰 경우</li>\n<li>gte : 컬럼 >= 조건, 크거나 같은 경우</li>\n<li>lte : 컬럼 &#x3C;= 조건, 값보다 작거나 같은 경우(여러번 사용할때는 and 조건으로 연결됨)</li>\n<li>lt : 컬럼 &#x3C; 조건, 값보다 작은 경우</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">Model<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>objects<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>컬럼__옵션<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>값<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># ex) id가 3보다 크고, test컬럼에 'hi'를 포함한 결과 찾기</span>\nModel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>objects<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>id__gt<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>text__icontains<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'hi'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nModel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>objects<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>id__gt<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> text__icontains<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'hi'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"foreignkey로-연결된-필드를-참조하는-경우\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#foreignkey%EB%A1%9C-%EC%97%B0%EA%B2%B0%EB%90%9C-%ED%95%84%EB%93%9C%EB%A5%BC-%EC%B0%B8%EC%A1%B0%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EA%B2%BD%EC%9A%B0\" aria-label=\"foreignkey로 연결된 필드를 참조하는 경우 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ForeignKey로 연결된 필드를 참조하는 경우</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">Model<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>objects<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>컬럼__옵션<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>값<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 글 작성자의 유저이름에 admin이 포함된 객체 반환</span>\nModel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>objects<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>user__name__icontain<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'admin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"요소-제외하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9A%94%EC%86%8C-%EC%A0%9C%EC%99%B8%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"요소 제외하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>요소 제외하기</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token comment\"># id가 1인 객체를 제외하고 불러오기</span>\nModel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>objects<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exclude<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token builtin\">id</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"개수-제한하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9C%EC%88%98-%EC%A0%9C%ED%95%9C%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"개수 제한하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>개수 제한하기</h3>\n<p>리스트 형태로 불러오기 때문에 리스트 슬라이스를 사용할 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 0부터 9번째 인덱스의 객체 불러오기</span>\nModel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>objects<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">all</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"정렬하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%95%EB%A0%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"정렬하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>정렬하기</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 오름차순</span>\nModel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>objects<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">all</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>order_by<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'created'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 내림차순</span>\nModel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>objects<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">all</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>order_by<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'-created'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"조건의-or-연결\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4%EC%9D%98-or-%EC%97%B0%EA%B2%B0\" aria-label=\"조건의 or 연결 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>조건의 or 연결</h3>\n<p>and(&#x26;), or(|), not(~) QuerySet의 filter에 사용하는 값은 기본적으로 무조건 and 연산이다.\nor 조건을 만들기 위에서는 Q 객체를 사용한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> django<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>db<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>models <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Q\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># comment가 'hi'나 'hello'로 시작하는 객체 반환</span>\nq <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Q<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>comment__startswith<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'hi'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> Q<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>comment__startswith<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'hello'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nModel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>objects<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>q<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Q 객체와 컬럼의 조건을 함께 사용할 때는 컬럼 조건이 항상 뒤에 와야 한다.</span>\nModel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>objects<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>q<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> id__gt<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"특정-컬럼의-값을-필터-조건에-포함하고-싶을-때\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B9%EC%A0%95-%EC%BB%AC%EB%9F%BC%EC%9D%98-%EA%B0%92%EC%9D%84-%ED%95%84%ED%84%B0-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4%EC%97%90-%ED%8F%AC%ED%95%A8%ED%95%98%EA%B3%A0-%EC%8B%B6%EC%9D%84-%EB%95%8C\" aria-label=\"특정 컬럼의 값을 필터 조건에 포함하고 싶을 때 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>특정 컬럼의 값을 필터 조건에 포함하고 싶을 때</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> django<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>db<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>models <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> F\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># comment에 title이 포함되어 있는 객체 반환</span>\nModel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>objects<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>text__icontains<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>F<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'title'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/Datebase/queryset","tagSlugs":["/tag/queryset/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-04-29","description":"queryset 다루기","tags":["queryset"],"title":"QuerySet 사용하기","socialImage":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/Datebase/queryset"}}}